{"tid":1591412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最近d浮屍案都好似由popo一手搞掂咁","createTime":"2019-09-24T06:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:53:10.000Z","uid":244845,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"840ac0743a1baa072ee426f5e28c5cd918188a40","tid":1591412,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有關跳海無論自殺或者失足墜海，無論碼頭跳海定船上跳海 通常黑警接到通知都會通知埋其他部門一齊處理<br />\n<br />\n好似今年2月15號 tst碼頭有個女人係天星小輪跳海<br />\n消防，水警，海事都要出動搜索 什至要飛行服務幫手<br />\n今年4月21號跳海 都係三個部門出動處理<br />\n<br />\n但最近發現浮屍 都好似只有popo自已出動搞掂<br />\n其他部門好似唔洗幫手咁<br />\n<br />\n加上 以我所知 發現浮屍都係由水警／消防處理<br />\n而海事係做交通管制<br />\n<br />\n雖然有機會係差佬評估完後覺得唔洗其他部門幫手<br />\n但如果單單都係咁 會唔會太可疑？<br />\n定只係海事處既職權唔夠處理最近既浮屍 所以冇人處理？"},{"pid":"ce53d602d8c49d629b18a44f804f06a8a7c374b9","tid":1591412,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q1RNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q1RNV6.jpg&h=227effc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93ac55f385b93d3768d6fb74cb2d83b0bd42b719","tid":1591412,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"全部消防都有去冇新聞報出嚟而己"},{"pid":"fa22e3b6e44fc38c98bed599b3476b42760d86ef","tid":1591412,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:51:16.000Z","msg":"[P牌推唔到] 924放映會 927 新屋嶺 928民陣集會 929 全球抗共 10.1國殤遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/edHpsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/edHpsS</a>"},{"pid":"052d095c83e5bd476a1a236abb48658547a09624","tid":1591412,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"［行動Po］10.1 創意玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"286c850c64adc946ef1ae39b326dcff349d4acd9","tid":1591412,"uid":244845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0